            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/21405345/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/21405345/" class="">第21页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/4371415/" class=" " title="lydia">lydia</a>
                (减肥季开始！)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="21405345">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">当前在一切之上的要务是反腐败，否则一切良好的设想和政策规划等都会在实践中付诸东流，甚或走向反面。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-09-28 16:41</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                当前在一切之上的要务是反腐败，否则一切良好的设想和政策规划等都会在实践中付诸东流，甚或走向反面。
